profile:
Elite Fire Protection has been providing fire safety solutions for over 25 years. Originally beginning as a team of three, Elite has since grown to a business of 50 employees across three locations. As a company started by three former firemen, Elite was created with the knowledge of the industry’s current standards and the desire to provide higher quality fire protection solutions than what was currently available.
Since then, we’ve dedicated ourselves to providing clients with the most trusted fire protection services in BC, and we take pride in the quality of service and technical knowledge our technicians offer.
Our head office, which operates out of Abbotsford, holds a fleet of service vehicles capable of installing, maintaining, and inspecting all manner of fire protection services and electrical installations. 
We have a proven history and rigorous commitment to following the guidelines set out by the BC Fire Code, National Fire Code of Canada, and local municipality bylaws, meaning our services can be trusted as consistent and reliable.

Elite Fire Protection is dedicated to the protection of occupants in the event of a fire, as well as to minimizing property loss and increasing awareness in emergency situations
